message.body: Have you heard from ####? I haven't yet
Nope havnt heard, ### asked if we were going though
Still havnt heard back from ####, but would still like to go out, how about you
I heard from ######. #### is working late tonight so I guess no go. I could go either way really. I have a paper to write
I'll leave it up to you, if you have a paper to write
Are you OK with a last minute decision? Let me see what kind of dent I can put in it in the next hour or so. Not really in the mood for lemon Hill though
I'm okay with last minute, where are you thinking
Sounds good, I'm gonna let ### know, maybe she will still come out
Do you mind if we raincheck this? I'm actually on a bit of a roll with this stupid paper and I'd like to finish it off tonight
